task.title: KV30F Pinouts
task.shortdesc: The pinout diagrams are also provided in an Excel file attached to this document:

step.cmd: Click the paperclip symbol on the left side of the PDF window.
Double-click on the Excel file to open it.

result.p: Many signals may be multiplexed onto a single pin. To determine what signals can be used on which pin, see the previous section.
